title: The Morning After Getting Cancelled
itunes:title: The Morning After Getting Cancelled
description: Kelly is back from New York to discuss her fun weekend in the city and shares a few slip ups she made along the way! She discusses cancel culture, how to teach your kids about making mistakes, and shares the story of the day she met Matthew & their first 24 hours together.The Morning After podcast is produced by ACTIONPARK MEDIA. Follow us on Social Media:@actionparkmediagroup @kbstafford89@themorningafter.kellystafford
